'''Heavy repeating cannons''' were stable ground-based [[Cannon/Legends|cannons]] used by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]. Such were deployed against the [[Naboo (people)/Legends|Naboo]] on [[Naboo/Legends|their]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] at the [[Time/Legends|time]] of [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|its]] invasion in [[32 BBY/Legends|32]] [[Galactic Standard Calendar|BBY]].

